ikk, bl.a. \u00abTil ungdommen\u00bb, \u00abFlagget\u00bb og \u00ab17. mai 1940\u00bb, samt skuespill: \u00abNederlaget\u00bb og \u00abV\u00e5r \u00e6re og v\u00e5r makt\u00bb.", "\u2022 Deltok som krigskorrespondent under et bombetokt over Berlin 2. desember 1943. Flyet han satt i, ble skutt ned, og Grieg omkom.", "Kilde: Store norske leksikon"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|magasin"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3aecf924c7fc764751c69f8ff10a8733c1977e558344669d3ec07e431df81f18"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-20T08:53:56.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u00abI dag st\u00e5r flaggstangen naken ...\u00bb, leste Nordahl Grieg over radioen fra Troms\u00f8 17. mai 1940. Men hva visste han om forholdene p\u00e5 Eidsvoll?"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/magasin/article10962967.ece/btkez0/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Folkevandring%20h%C3%B8yoppl%C3%B8selig12323.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5273afff2d74c3e79a82adb17ddd90dc774c239b.jpg?591618a9"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Sto flaggstangen naken? -adressa.no", "P\u00e5stander om flagging", "Om flagging i Trondheim", "Nordahl Griegs dikt", "17. mai 1940", "Nordahl Grieg (1902 - 1943)"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "5273afff2d74c3e79a82adb17ddd90dc774c239b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["70 \u00e5r siden frigj\u00f8ringen", "Ukeadressa"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "70 \u00e5r siden frigj\u00f8ringen,Ukeadressa"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "magasin"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["naken", "dag", "flagg", "mai", "flaggstangen", "flaggstangen naken"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["diktaren", "ukeadressa", "flagg